That said, I would also be happier if...<br>
<br>
1) Foliage Shield were fixed duration like our Improved Superior Camo. Make it ten minutes.<br>
<br>
2) We received a high-end DOT at 59 (we get direct damage spells at 54 (Blizzard and Scoriae), 55 (Exile Summoned), 56 (Breath of Karana), 57 (Frost), 58 (Fist of Karana) and 59 (Wildfire) and the lame 60th Moonfire) -- Forget Moonfire and give us an upgrade to Winged Death (Death from Above hehe) that is 2500-3000 damage.<br>
<br>
3) Nature's Recovery were group-based.<br>
<br>
4) Make our next epic weapon something more useful for a group please like the reverse healing damage shield idea.<br>
